243
00:13:40,622 --> 00:13:46,591
Ikaw mismo ang tumawag sa kompanya ng card para i-block.

244
00:13:46,614 --> 00:13:49,559
Naiintindihan ko po.

245
00:13:49,582 --> 00:13:50,582
Saan po ba ang embahada ng Japan?

246
00:13:50,606 --> 00:13:55,395
Ire-issue po ng pasaporte, 'di ba?

247
00:13:55,418 --> 00:13:58,851
Ibibigay ko po ang mapa.

248
00:13:58,874 --> 00:13:59,874
Nawala rin ang susi ng bahay sa loob ng bag, kaya hindi ako makapasok sa kwarto.

249
00:13:59,898 --> 00:14:00,898
Pwede mo ba akong ibigay ang contact ng may-ari ng bahay?

250
00:14:00,921 --> 00:14:01,921
Wala akong cellphone, kaya hindi ko alam ang numero.

251
00:14:01,944 --> 00:14:05,286
Naku, ang hirap naman.

252
00:14:05,309 --> 00:14:09,107
Pwede ko ba ipatawag ang pamilya ko?

253
00:14:09,131 --> 00:14:14,466
Oo, gamitin mo na lang itong telepono.

254
00:14:14,489 --> 00:14:17,489
Tagpo 9: Pagkikita kasama ang mga Kaibigan

255
00:14:17,489 --> 00:14:23,756
Hey, next week ba ang day-off mo? Tara, lumabas tayo.

256
00:14:23,779 --> 00:14:26,018
Sige, ayos lang.

257
00:14:26,041 --> 00:14:27,041
Saan tayo pupunta?

258
00:14:27,064 --> 00:14:28,064
May bagong café, gusto ko sanang puntahan.

259
00:14:28,087 --> 00:14:30,721
Sige, okay lang.

260
00:14:30,744 --> 00:14:31,744
O sige, ibigay mo nga ang LINE mo.

261
00:14:31,767 --> 00:14:32,767
Oo,

262
00:14:32,790 --> 00:14:37,058
I-scan mo ang QR code.

263
00:14:37,082 --> 00:14:40,115
Naidagdag ko na.

264
00:14:40,138 --> 00:14:43,675
Ipadala ko na lang mamaya ang details.

265
00:14:43,699 --> 00:14:44,699
Pasensya na,

266
00:14:44,722 --> 00:14:45,722
Sandali lang.

267
00:14:45,745 --> 00:14:49,379
Hindi ko mabuhol ang sintas ng sapatos.

268
00:14:49,402 --> 00:14:52,735
Tahimik lang, okay lang.

269
00:14:52,758 --> 00:14:56,391
Nauuhaw ako.

270
00:14:56,414 --> 00:14:57,414
Pwede ba tayong dumaan sa convenience store?

271
00:14:57,438 --> 00:15:00,188
Sige.

272
00:15:00,211 --> 00:15:05,200
Ah, pwede mo ba akong pahiram ng pera?

273
00:15:05,223 --> 00:15:06,223
Ha? Magkano?

274
00:15:06,246 --> 00:15:07,246
Limandaan lang.

275
00:15:07,269 --> 00:15:11,028
Naiwan ko kasi ang wallet.

276
00:15:11,052 --> 00:15:13,885
Ang kulit mo talaga.

277
00:15:13,908 --> 00:15:14,908
Eto, limandaan.

278
00:15:14,931 --> 00:15:17,365
Salamat.

279
00:15:17,388 --> 00:15:21,374
Babayaran kita bukas.

280
00:15:21,397 --> 00:15:22,397
Ang sarap talaga ng cake na 'to!

281
00:15:22,421 --> 00:15:23,421
Talaga?

282
00:15:23,444 --> 00:15:24,444
Pwede ko ba subukan 'to?

283
00:15:24,467 --> 00:15:27,062
Sige.

284
00:15:27,085 --> 00:15:30,352
Eto, 'wag kang matakot, ha.

285
00:15:30,375 --> 00:15:31,375
Ang sarap!

286
00:15:31,398 --> 00:15:32,398
Gusto mo ba subukan ang pancake ko?

287
00:15:32,421 --> 00:15:33,421
Gusto ko! Ah, ipadala mo nga ang picture.

288
00:15:33,445 --> 00:15:35,843
Sige.

289
00:15:35,866 --> 00:15:39,370
Ini-send ko na sa LINE mo.

290
00:15:39,393 --> 00:15:41,659
Salamat.

291
00:15:41,682 --> 00:15:42,682
Huwag mong sasabihin sa iba ang tungkol sa tindahan na 'to, ha?

292
00:15:42,706 --> 00:15:44,972
Sige, okay lang.

293
00:15:44,995 --> 00:15:48,562
Sikreto lang natin 'to, ah?

294
00:15:48,585 --> 00:15:51,585
Tagpo 10: Paghahanda at Pagkumpirma para sa Pulong

295
00:15:51,585 --> 00:15:54,618
Kumusta na, ingat.

296
00:15:54,641 --> 00:15:57,908
Naririnig mo ba ako?

297
00:15:57,931 --> 00:16:01,690
Oo, naririnig kita.

298
00:16:01,713 --> 00:16:03,904
Excuse me po,

299
00:16:03,928 --> 00:16:07,647
Mangyaring buksan ang iyong mikropono.

300
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:10,737
Ay, pasensya na.

301
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:13,919
Binuksan ko na ngayon.

302
00:16:13,943 --> 00:16:17,009
Okay lang.

303
00:16:17,032 --> 00:16:20,999
Simulan na natin ang pulong.

304
00:16:21,022 --> 00:16:26,089
Tignan natin ang datos ng benta ngayong linggo.

305
00:16:26,112 --> 00:16:31,101
Pwede mo ba ibahagi ang iyong screen?

306
00:16:31,124 --> 00:16:35,163
Oo, sandali lang.

307
00:16:35,187 --> 00:16:38,420
Okay na ba ito?

308
00:16:38,443 --> 00:16:42,276
Hindi pa kita nakikita.

309
00:16:42,299 --> 00:16:46,937
Pwede ko ba uliting ikonek muli?

310
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:49,694
Naiintindihan ko po.

311
00:16:49,717 --> 00:16:52,386
Naghihintay lang ako.

312
00:16:52,409 --> 00:16:55,275
Pasensya na sa paghihintay.

313
00:16:55,298 --> 00:17:00,565
Ang iyong boses, medyo malayo pa rin.

314
00:17:00,588 --> 00:17:03,255
Talaga ba?

315
00:17:03,278 --> 00:17:08,657
Mangyaring magsalita nang mas malakas.

316
00:17:08,681 --> 00:17:12,416
Sinusubukan ko ang mikropono.

317
00:17:12,439 --> 00:17:14,814
Kumusta na?

318
00:17:14,838 --> 00:17:19,551
Oo, ngayon ay malinaw na.

319
00:17:19,575 --> 00:17:22,342
Mabuti naman.

320
00:17:22,365 --> 00:17:26,964
Pwede ko ba i-record ang meeting na ito?

321
00:17:26,987 --> 00:17:31,258
Oo, walang problema.

322
00:17:31,281 --> 00:17:36,619
Ilagay ang mahalagang URL sa chat.

323
00:17:36,643 --> 00:17:40,914
Ini-send ko na ang link.

324
00:17:40,937 --> 00:17:43,970
Nakita ko na.

325
00:17:43,993 --> 00:17:48,775
I-email mo na lang ang detalye mamaya.

326
00:17:48,798 --> 00:17:51,732
Naiintindihan ko.

327
00:17:51,755 --> 00:17:56,488
Isasama ko rin ang tala ng pulong sa email.

328
00:17:56,511 --> 00:17:59,544
Salamat, hinihintay ko na.